Client Referral Program
How would you like to get 50% OFF your next Haircut & Style?
It’s as easy as 1, 2, 3!
1. Ask your stylist for the Client Referral Program Cards (Fill it out).
2. Refer a client to your favorite stylist. Your referred client will receive 50% off a haircut and style. (They must bring in the Client Referral Card in order for offer to be valid.)
3. You will receive a 50% off your next haircut and style postcard on the mail.

Offer must be used within 3 months. No exceptions.
