Hair Shaping and Styling - Mitchell Christopher Salon












































 





Skip to content






 









Hair Shaping and Styling 




Complimentary Consultations – Complimentary (15-30 minutes)
Not sure what you are looking for? Schedule a complimentary consultation with any of our our talented stylists. Great communication between client and stylist will ensure you leave our salon feeling and looking the best that you can be.
Women’s Hair Shaping – from $40-55
Start out with a consultation with your stylist to make you sure your needs are met. A women’s hair shaping includes a cleansing of your hair with only the best haircare products available. Proceed with a precision shaping or perhaps a razor cut is what you’re looking for. Finish with a blow dry and style and a basic knowledge of how to maintain your new look at home.
Men’s Hair Cut – from $30-40
Have you noticed? More and more men are needing and wanting the expertise and precision cutting of a hairdresser? We at Mitchell Christopher Salon fill that need for many of our male clientele. A haircut include a full cleansing of the hair with Redken For Men Shampoo and Conditioner… a line of haircare products solely dedicated to a male driven clientele. followed by a precision haircutting or clipper cutting… finished off with a style to fit your everyday lifestyle and needs.











Bang Trim – from $5
A quick trim for bangs that are getting a little too long.
Styling – from $30
Blow Dry and Style, light curling iron
Kid’s Hair Cutting (under 12) – from $25-35
A hair cut just for the little ones, make them feel special like Mom and Dad. Let our stylists pamper your kids with a great hair cut and style fit for a princess or a prince. Little girls love the braids… Little boys enjoy the stylish look with gel or pomade products in their hair.
Formal/Evening Styling – from $70
We have very talented hairdressers that will ensure you look the very best for your event.















