Team 




Our creative team of professionals are all highly trained and experienced. They are dedicated to providing you with the latest techniques and trends to suit your needs. Prices will vary on the service professional.











Mariefel Westa
Salon Owner/Stylist
With over 25 years experience in the hair industry, Mariefel will take your color and hair design needs to the next level. Her dedication to education is unsurpassed. As an educator and a certified colorist, she has taken her field of expertise to the highest level. Her style approach is low maintenance hair fashion that is easily recreated outside the salon. She believes in creating a style/color that will work with your lifestyle.






Dean
Salon Owner/Stylist
With over 20 years experience as a stylist, Dean has mastered the art of Women’s Hair Design along with Men’s Hair Shaping and men’s natural grey blending using Redken Men’s Camo Color. He also has a strong clientele of “color/highlighted” guests. Dean is excellent in helping to remove weight and reshape thick hair. He will show you quick and easy techniques to style your curly hair. He believes in honing his skills as an artist on a regular basis through continuing education.. If you enjoy the artistic interpretation of a talented male hairdresser, Dean is your Expert!


















Chris
Stylist
With over 20 years experience in the industry, Chris enjoys the hair fashions of today. She also enjoys doing manicures and pedicures specializing in the Shellac procedure. Her signature or style is “conservative/trendy”. If you would like to turn up your current style or hair color a notch… then Chris is your expert!






Rachel Enos
Stylist
