• Hair Treats Extensions Certified
• Eyelash Extensions Certified
“As a Redken Certified Colorist, I pride myself in delivering the highest quality of haircare service to my salon guests. I enjoy enhancing the beauty that is within you. My specialty services include balayage/ombre highlighting, specialty/creative hair coloring, rich, revived radiant reds, bridal and special occasion styling, makeup, eyelash extensions, and hair extensions. I enjoy creating flawless, seamless, wearable styles that suit your every day needs.”
